            "name": "Culinary Alchemy",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The azarpal knows the formulas for all common and uncommon alchemical foods of its level or lower in *Treasure Vault* without needing a formula book. A typical azarpal carries about 700 gp of alchemical food.",
